OL,3,CMan who stabbed friend believed he was
OL,4,Cacting in self defence, court hears
OL,6,FOn the fifth day of the trial, Dr
OL,7,FPanchu Xavier, a consultant forensic
OL,8,Fpsychiatrist at Ashworth High Secure
OL,9,FHospital, where the defendant is being
OL,10,Ftreated for schizophrenia, told the
OL,11,Fcourt he believed Thomas had been
OL,12,Fpsychotic "for many months" before the
OL,13,Ffatal incident, and had formed the
OL,14,Fopinion his life was under threat.
OL,16,F"My view is that he was convinced he
OL,17,Fwas going to come to harm", Dr Xavier
OL,18,Fsaid.
OL,20,F"If that is what you think, you are
OL,21,Fgoing to try to eliminate that threat."
