OL,3,CMan who stabbed friend believed he was
OL,4,Cacting in self defence, court hears
OL,6,F"In his mind, that's why he behaved as
OL,7,Fhe did. He felt threatened by his best
OL,8,Ffriend and that's why he responded as
OL,9,Fhe did."
OL,11,FThe trial has previously heard that Mr
OL,12,FThomas initially stabbed Mr Bush in
OL,13,Fhis bedroom, before chasing him down
OL,14,Fthe stairs of the 3 storey house they
OL,15,Fshared in Cardiff where the assault
OL,16,Fcontinued.
OL,18,FMr Bush sustained serious wounds to
OL,19,Fhis neck and died at the scene.
